_sText:
This map was meant for a higher purpose, it was meant to be added along with pirate_wars and a number of other mini-games to a big mini-game map.

However due to other priorities i had to abandon the project.

This map is nothing more than a very first alpha and is only just able to run.

I'm releasing it as i'm sure some people can get maybe 20 minutes of fun out of it.

This map has a max of 5 spawns per team.

PLEASE DO NOT RATE THIS MAP AS ITS SIMPLY A FAILED ATTEMPTED AT A BETTER MAP.
